{"tid":1707973,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"廉署拘21人包括2助理練馬師及4馬房職員懷疑涉貪","createTime":"2019-11-11T12:26:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T17:05:22.000Z","uid":240362,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"b8aaf7ee1c829b3e456f20ef25a149275ae50d87","tid":1707973,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:26:48.000Z","msg":"廉政公署拘捕共21名人士，包括兩名馬會助理練馬師及4名馬房職員，懷疑涉及貪污，提供賽馬的保密資料，以協助經營非法外圍賭博及操控馬匹。<br />\n<br />\n廉署表示上星期六展開行動，在荃灣一個住宅大廈搗破一個外圍投注集團，行動中亦拘捕15名涉及貪污和從事收受非法投注的人士。廉署說調查仍在進行，現階段不會再作進一步評論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1491427-20191111.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1491427-20191111.htm&d=LL%2BPOpKvGkF1h1mPLRhV%2B2LZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=efd52e18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1491427-20191111.htm&h=cd7a9f89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1491427-20191111.htm</a>"},{"pid":"47abbb6d84a6fb427742d578a5eb717481242d6f","tid":1707973,"uid":132587,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:27:30.000Z","msg":"得閒就查黑警啦搞埋曬d無聊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a2bb77e2817c3472e00766535a64330c933327","tid":1707973,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:27:38.000Z","msg":"呀鄧呢？"},{"pid":"a700cc45a42315c63288c7d54aaa1d87a4c789ce","tid":1707973,"uid":13333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:30:05.000Z","msg":"極速前進？"},{"pid":"bc1263a13ed7e5088aa70e7801e11381afb85d41","tid":1707973,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96a2bb77e2817c3472e00766535a64330c933327","tid":1707973,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:27:38.000Z","msg":"呀鄧呢？